# Skills You Will Build

After practicing this routine for **2–3 months**, you will master:

* Core **JavaScript**
* DOM manipulation
* API calls
* Async programming
* Problem solving

Then you can easily move to:

* React
* Node.js
* Express.js

This leads to becoming a **full-stack developer using the MERN Stack**.

